<component type="desktop">
  <id>org.kiwix.desktop</id>
  <name>Kiwix</name>
  <summary>View offline content</summary>
  <developer_name>The Kiwix Foundation</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>
      Kiwix is an offline reader - meaning that it allows you to check text or video that is normally only available on the internet.
    </p>
    <p>
      We turn various online educational contents (such as Wikipedia, for example) into ZIM files, and these can be opened by Kiwix even if you are no connection whatsoever.
    </p>
  </description>
